{"tid":1385119,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"踢爆縱暴派 屈警六謠言 謠言：催淚彈點燃手推車，順下坡滑向警方  事實：暴徒縱火攻擊警方防線","createTime":"2019-07-30T04:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T04:52:44.000Z","uid":17232,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e5e49d476ad9cfaf27ff68cfb5aa9b2608a3a32e","tid":1385119,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:10:05.000Z","msg":"香港文匯報梳理了暴徒及縱暴派為掩飾暴行杜撰的各種「離奇情節」，為讀者還原上周六（27日）及周日（28日）暴徒在元朗及上環攻擊警方、滋擾市民的真面目：他們在安老院前發動暴亂，卻聲稱警方「刻意」向安老院施放催淚彈；他們暴力毀壞路邊私家車，卻構陷「車輛與中聯辦有關」，無理地「合理化」自己暴力毀壞私家車的暴行。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">謠言：催淚彈點燃手推車，順下坡滑向警方<br />\n事實：暴徒縱火攻擊警方防線<br />\n<br />\n連登仔美化暴徒行徑，稱周日在上環的縱火事件，是因「手推車的紙皮被警方的催淚彈火光點燃引起燃燒，又由於手推車位於斜路，令手推車由斜路高處滑到警方防線，因而引起誤會。」<br />\n<br />\n然而，真相卻是暴徒在永樂街縱火後，又在西港城外點燃裝滿紙皮的手推車，並推向警方防線，警方隨後發射催淚彈反擊。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2019/07/30/HS1907300020.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2019%2F07%2F30%2FHS1907300020.htm&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmIyYtkWzW%2FBkyQE6eFpzr100%3D&h=173b47f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2019/07/30/HS1907300020.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6543186989f59bb760e1144e0bfcd568c02ed34d","tid":1385119,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P04cs6q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP04cs6q.png&h=f6e771fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e486a7e0cfdb68d6def281d0bb06596fd6f18ca4","tid":1385119,"uid":208452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T0