<br />\n幫手推下呢個po唔該<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雙普選比獨立調查更重要<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379266</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"c4748a5e7ecee80040f32f23e889522891207d2f","tid":1385119,"uid":17232,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:18:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">踢爆可恥文匯報 屈示威者六謠言</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n謠言：示威者縱火攻擊警方防線<br />\n事實：催淚彈點燃手推車，順下坡滑向警方<br />\n<br />\n謠言：示威者阻礙警方執法<br />\n事實：示威者撤退，警方卻施放催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n謠言：示威者在安老院前製造騷亂<br />\n事實：警方向安老院投擲催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n謠言：警方解釋棍繩鬆脫滑出膠索帶<br />\n事實：警棍疑套金屬環增加殺傷力<br />\n<br />\n謠言：私家車與中聯辦無關，慘遭示威者損毀<br />\n事實：黑色私家車「與中聯辦有關」，載有大量木棍、軍刀及鐵通<br />\n<br />\n謠言：正義婆婆要示威者離開<br />\n事實：警察欺負婆婆"},{"pid":"72137a3bbba177cb43ad93db105725e3e03bc066","tid":1385119,"uid":17232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:21:13.000Z","msg":"強烈譴責文匯報作出不實指控，明顯是極少數有預謀，有組織的有心人士抹黑示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7d0a4811cb99ad3181c9ad35c6fa4f97d61aa4","tid":1385119,"uid":229296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4001770e79f883fe666f3f36108657cc320c18","tid":1385119,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a7d0a4811cb99ad3181c9ad35c6fa4f97d61aa4","tid":1385119,"uid":229296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:26:15.000Z","msg":"堅"},{"pid":"9462d1add7aaaa4a88c08dd87652d3b38a4d630d","tid":1385119,"uid":49525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:52:44.000Z","msg":"又作故事"}]}